refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public intGmagickPixel::getcolorvaluequantum intcolor
Retrieves the value of the specified color channel as a raw quantum value, ranging from 0 to the maximum quantum value (QuantumRange) of the underlying GraphicsMagick build, rather than the normalized 0 to 1 range returned by GmagickPixel::getcolorvalue.

&reftitle.parameters;


  color


    The channel to read, specified as one of the Gmagick channel constants.
